            <title>vivo 与中国摄影家协会签署长期战略合作备忘录：共同探索制定手机影像行业标准</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/807/887.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/807/887.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
            <updated>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 15:01:35 GMT</updated>
                
                
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <div class="tougao-user">感谢IT之家网友 <a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D2158026" rel="nofollow">Autumn_Dream</a> 的线索投递！</div>
